OL,3,CPolicing chief threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover no confidence motion after protest
OL,6,FA policing chief is threatening to
OL,7,Ftake legal action after she faced a
OL,8,Fvote of no confidence over attending a
OL,9,Fprotest against asylum seekers being
OL,10,Fhoused at a military site in
OL,11,FCrowborough.
OL,13,FSussex Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,14,F(PCC) Katy Bourne is demanding for the
OL,15,Fformal criticism be withdrawn and for
OL,16,Fa public apology to be issued after
OL,17,Fshe was censured in a non-binding
OL,18,Fmotion for attending a march at the
OL,19,Fsite in November.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
