PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773061887
OL,3,CPolicing chief threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover no confidence motion after protest
OL,6,FA series of protests have been held
OL,7,Fagainst the use of Crowborough
OL,8,FTraining Camp to accommodate more than
OL,9,F500 men while their asylum claims are
OL,10,Fprocessed.
OL,12,FPassed by a majority vote, the Sussex
OL,13,FPolice and Crime Panel said it has
OL,14,F"lost confidence" in the commissioner
OL,15,Fand her conduct after attending a
OL,16,Fprotest on November 8 and her comments
OL,17,Fon Radio Sussex on December 30
OL,18,F"calling for asylum seekers to be
OL,19,Ffitted with electronic tags" as well
OL,20,Fas other actions on social media.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@QO]zD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
