OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773061887
OL,3,CPolicing chief threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover no confidence motion after protest
OL,6,F"Her lack of impartiality has brought
OL,7,Fthe office of Commissioner and
OL,8,Fpolicing into disrepute," the motion
OL,9,Fread.
OL,11,F"We therefore censure her for her
OL,12,Factions."
OL,14,FMinutes of the meeting on 30 January
OL,15,Fshow Ms Bourne, an elected official,
OL,16,Fexpressed her motivations had purely
OL,17,Fbeen to engage with local residents
OL,18,Fand hear their concerns, and that she
OL,19,Fstated she felt harassed for simply
OL,20,Fdoing her job.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@YO]sD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773061887
OL,3,CPolicing chief threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover no confidence motion after protest
OL,6,FThe minutes also said she suggested
OL,7,Fher interactions with social media had
OL,8,Fbeen in a personal capacity and some
OL,9,Fof her comments had been
OL,10,Fmisrepresented.
OL,12,FThe PCC chief executive and monitoring
OL,13,Fofficer Mark Streater also asked for
OL,14,Fit to be put on record that he did not
OL,15,Frecognise the motion as a formal duty
OL,16,Fof the panel and awaited a report from
OL,17,Fthe panel's clerk to justify the
OL,18,Fdecision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773061887
OL,3,CPolicing chief threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover no confidence motion after protest
OL,6,FThe document said advice from the
OL,7,Fofficer of the clerk confirmed in the
OL,8,Fmeeting it was within the panel's
OL,9,Fremit to vote on any motions which had
OL,10,Fbeen proposed and seconded, but it
OL,11,Fwould not be binding and the PCC would
OL,12,Fhave a right to respond.
OL,14,FA spokeswoman for the PCC's office
OL,15,Fsaid: "I can confirm that the Sussex
OL,16,FPolice and Crime Commissioner has
OL,17,Ftaken legal advice and instructed our
OL,18,Fsolicitors to contact the legal
OL,19,Fadvisor to the Sussex Police and Crime
OL,20,FPanel (PCP).
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
