OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773061887
OL,3,CPolicing chief threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover no confidence motion after protest
OL,6,F"This is to issue a notice of proposed
OL,7,Fjudicial review of the decision of the
OL,8,FPCP to censure the Sussex Police and
OL,9,FCrime Commissioner at the meeting at
OL,10,FCounty Hall in Lewes on 30th January."
OL,12,FThe spokeswoman said the PCC is
OL,13,Fadvised this procedure is outside of
OL,14,Fthe panel's statutory authority and
OL,15,Fwas in breach of Articles 10 and 11,
OL,16,Ffreedom of expression and freedom of
OL,17,Fassembly and association, of the
OL,18,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights.
OL,20,FThe Sussex Police and Crime Panel have
OL,21,Fbeen contacted for comment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]
